---
<!-- WHICH ONE FITS SECTION -->
<section id="which-one-fits" class="relative border-b border-line">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 sm:px-8 py-20 sm:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> Which One Fits</span>
      <h2 class="mt-5 text-[2rem] sm:text-[2.6rem] leading-[1.05] font-bold">
        Choose the Right Starting Point
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
      <div class="card p-7 sm:p-8 flex flex-col gap-4">
        <div class="font-display font-semibold text-[0.78rem] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Choose the Sprint if…</div>
        <p class="text-[1rem] text-text-soft leading-relaxed">
          Your site is already live but you know it could be converting better. You want a paid review and cleanup before committing to a larger build.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-2">
          <a href="#apply" class="btn-ghost">
            Start My Sprint
            <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-7 sm:p-8 flex flex-col gap-4 border-accent/40">
        <div class="font-display font-semibold text-[0.78rem] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Choose the Wizard if…</div>
        <p class="text-[1rem] text-text-soft leading-relaxed">
          You're ready to replace a basic form with a guided quote or booking flow that presents packages, captures better leads, and helps customers take the next step.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-2">
          <a href="#apply" class="btn-primary">
            Apply for a Wizard Build
            <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-10 max-w-3xl text-[1.02rem] sm:text-[1.08rem] leading-relaxed text-text">
      Not sure? Start with the Sprint. If the Wizard is the right move, <span class="text-accent font-medium">we'll tell you exactly why</span>.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- /WHICH ONE FITS SECTION -->
